564
00:35:53,680 --> 00:35:55,580
Dia tinggal di dalam sini...

565
00:35:55,580 --> 00:35:57,320
...di dalam ubun-ubun.

566
00:35:57,320 --> 00:35:59,180
Di lobus oksipital.

567
00:35:59,190 --> 00:36:01,290
Di dalam otak indah itu...

568
00:36:01,290 --> 00:36:03,420
...tersimpan rahasia...

569
00:36:03,420 --> 00:36:06,790
...untuk memahami kegelapan jiwa manusia.

570
00:36:06,790 --> 00:36:08,130
Dan jika sepuluh otak itu...

571
00:36:08,130 --> 00:36:09,760
...digabung menjadi satu...

572
00:36:09,760 --> 00:36:11,360
...tidak segelap seperti yang ada...

573
00:36:11,370 --> 00:36:12,460
...di dalam sini,...

574
00:36:12,470 --> 00:36:13,830
...di bagian terlucu...,

575
00:36:13,830 --> 00:36:15,500
...di kepala.

576
00:36:27,310 --> 00:36:28,350
"Korban ditemukan dalam keadaan telanjang.

577
00:36:28,350 --> 00:36:30,820
"Temuan awal menunjukkan...

578
00:36:30,820 --> 00:36:32,380
"...bahwa proses menguliti terjadi...

579
00:36:32,390 --> 00:36:33,520
"...saat korban masih bernapas."

580
00:36:36,720 --> 00:36:37,490
Kit!

581
00:36:37,490 --> 00:36:40,630
Alma!

582
00:36:40,630 --> 00:36:41,690
Tolong aku!

583
00:36:41,700 --> 00:36:43,360
Alma!

584
00:36:46,530 --> 00:36:47,970
Kau mengirisnya dari kaki.

585
00:36:50,870 --> 00:36:52,500
Mau kau apakan kulitnya?

586
00:36:56,480 --> 00:36:58,310
Aku tidak bermaksud menghakimi,
Tn. Walker.

587
00:36:58,310 --> 00:37:01,080
Aku hanya tertarik pada metodologi.

588
00:37:01,080 --> 00:37:03,220
Apa ini?

589
00:37:03,220 --> 00:37:05,150
Mirip seperti tumor.

590
00:37:46,190 --> 00:37:48,630
Tn. Walker?

591
00:37:48,630 --> 00:37:49,530
Tn. Walker?

592
00:37:57,470 --> 00:37:59,540
Kau mempertaruhkan segalanya.

593
00:37:59,540 --> 00:38:01,110
Segalanya.

594
00:38:01,110 --> 00:38:02,370
Reputasi kita,...

595
00:38:02,380 --> 00:38:03,440
...hasil kerja...

596
00:38:03,440 --> 00:38:04,780
...dari Kepala Pendeta kita,...

597
00:38:04,780 --> 00:38:06,410
...semua mimpinya akan masa depan.

598
00:38:06,410 --> 00:38:09,050
Aku sudah biasa dinilai buruk, Suster.

599
00:38:09,050 --> 00:38:10,550
Sudah biasa?

600
00:38:10,550 --> 00:38:11,720
Seperti terlalu banyak makan kue?

601
00:38:11,720 --> 00:38:13,080
Itu maksudmu, Suster?

602
00:38:13,090 --> 00:38:17,090
Nona Winters membuatku bingung.

603
00:38:17,090 --> 00:38:19,660
Mungkin ini dosaku,
mungkin kepercayaanku pada dirimu...

604
00:38:19,660 --> 00:38:21,290
...hanyalah keangkuhan.

605
00:38:21,300 --> 00:38:22,630
Tidak, kau bukan pendosa, Suster.

606
00:38:22,630 --> 00:38:25,130
Aku mengasihimu, memanjakanmu.

607
00:38:25,130 --> 00:38:27,670
Aku menolak melihat apa yang
orang lain lihat.

608
00:38:27,670 --> 00:38:28,830
Saat mereka bilang...

609
00:38:28,840 --> 00:38:30,670
<i>..kau bodoh,...</i>

610
00:38:30,670 --> 00:38:32,500
Aku menyangkalnya, karena...

611
00:38:32,510 --> 00:38:34,440
...kau lebih suci dari yang lainnya.

612
00:38:34,440 --> 00:38:37,040
Dosaku tidak terlalu besar, Suster.

613
00:38:50,760 --> 00:38:52,660
Hukum aku, Suster. Kumohon!

614
00:38:53,490 --> 00:38:56,090
Aku sangat lemah dan bodoh, Suster.

615
00:38:56,100 --> 00:38:57,460
Sangat bodoh.

616
00:39:02,030 --> 00:39:03,870
Bangun dan pergilah.

617
00:39:03,870 --> 00:39:05,170
Aku tak punya waktu untuk ini.

618
00:39:07,640 --> 00:39:08,640
Kau terlalu baik padaku, Suster.

619
00:39:08,640 --> 00:39:10,680
Jika aku mendengarmu,...

620
00:39:10,680 --> 00:39:12,310
...menyebut dirimu bodoh lagi.

621
00:39:12,310 --> 00:39:13,680
Aku akan memukulmu sampai berdarah.

622
00:39:38,540 --> 00:39:40,640
Kau sudah bangun.

623
00:39:40,640 --> 00:39:41,840
Melegakan sekali.

624
00:39:41,840 --> 00:39:44,810
Apa yang terjadi?

625
00:39:44,810 --> 00:39:46,540
Kau mengalami kecelakaan.

626
00:39:47,650 --> 00:39:49,550
Ada yang menyerangku.

627
00:39:49,550 --> 00:39:50,980
Penulis sepertimu,...

628
00:39:50,980 --> 00:39:53,550
...punya banyak imajinasi.

629
00:39:53,550 --> 00:39:55,590
Kau rela bergelut.

630
00:39:55,590 --> 00:39:56,860
Lepaskan benda ini dari tubuhku.

631
00:39:56,860 --> 00:39:59,520
